  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

  <h2>Controller</h2>
  <p>Zoe Barossi, address as listed in the <a href="legal.html">Legal Notice</a>.</p>

  <h2>What we do NOT do</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>No cookies. No trackers. No analytics.</li>
    <li>No advertising pixels, no retargeting.</li>
    <li>No newsletter sign-up without your explicit consent.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Hosting</h2>
  <p>This website is hosted by <strong>statichost.eu</strong> (Variable Object Assignment, Stockholm/Sweden; server location Helsinki/Finland). Statichost stores no personal data, no IP addresses, no access logs.</p>

  <h2>Getting in touch</h2>
  <p>If you send an email (<a href="mailto:hallo@zoebarossi.com">hallo@zoebarossi.com</a> or <a href="mailto:sponsoring@zoebarossi.com">sponsoring@zoebarossi.com</a>), your details will be stored to process your request. Legal basis: Art. 6 para. 1 lit. b GDPR. The data will be deleted once the request has been handled, unless legal retention obligations require otherwise.</p>

  <h2>Social media links</h2>
  <p>This site contains links to Instagram, Twitch, YouTube and possibly other services. Data is transmitted to the respective provider only when you click on a link. The privacy policies of the respective provider then apply.</p>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>You have the right to access, rectification, deletion, restriction of processing, data portability and objection. To exercise these rights, please contact the email address above.</p>

  <p>You also have the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority. The competent authority is the state data protection commissioner of your federal state.</p>

  <h2>SSL encryption</h2>
  <p>For security reasons, this website uses SSL encryption. You can recognise it by the lock icon in your browser's address bar.</p>

  <p style="margin-top: 3rem; font-size: 12px; color: var(--color-secondary); letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase;">Last updated: April 2026</p>
